rows.label: qst101803_msg001
rows.name: Temp implementation of LIST_QST101803

rows.label: qst101803_msg002
rows.name: Jizo is already dead.

rows.label: qst101803_msg0001
rows.name: Possah! I'm home, mo.

rows.label: qst101803_msg0002
rows.name: ...Who are you, mo?

rows.label: qst101803_msg0003
rows.name:
I've lost a little weight, so you
can't tell, mo? It's Jizo, mo!

rows.label: qst101803_msg0004
rows.name: Jizo...

rows.label: qst101803_msg0005
rows.name: Jizo is no longer in Alst, mo...

rows.label: qst101803_msg0006
rows.name:
He headed to a scary place called
Badfella's Cave Fort... and didn't
come back for days and days, mo.

rows.label: qst101803_msg0007
rows.name:
I came back, mo~ Please look
closely at Jizo's face, mo.

rows.label: qst101803_msg0008
rows.name: *stare*

rows.label: qst101803_msg0009
rows.name:
Jizo was short and chubby,
and fluffy and puffy, mo...

rows.label: qst101803_msg0010
rows.name:
This skinny, dirty
thing isn't Jizo, mo!

rows.label: qst101803_msg0011
rows.name:
Playing a cruel joke on a
heartbroken Possah, mo!

rows.label: qst101803_msg0012
rows.name: [ML:Feeling kind=Anger ]G-G-G-GASP!

rows.label: qst101803_msg0013
rows.name: I-I'm... Somehow okay, mo.

rows.label: qst101803_msg0014
rows.name:
I lost so much weight because
I didn't move, mo...

rows.label: qst101803_msg0015
rows.name:
But I'm sure she'll remember if she
sees me with my Blade, Vahsah, mo.

rows.label: qst101803_msg0016
rows.name:
We were good friends who played
together with Possah, mo.

rows.label: qst101803_msg0017
rows.name: ...Vahsah isn't here either, mo.

rows.label: qst101803_msg0018
rows.name: Where did she go, mo...?

rows.label: qst101803_msg0019
rows.name: [ML:Feeling kind=Think ]Vahsah... Where are you, mo...

rows.label: qst101803_msg0020
rows.name: Ah! I've got it, mo!

rows.label: qst101803_msg0021
rows.name:
She's in the city...
She's in Fons Maim, mo!

rows.label: qst101803_msg0022
rows.name:
She must be looking for
someone to help Jizo, mo.

rows.label: qst101803_msg0023
rows.name: [ML:Feeling kind=Think ]Vahsah... Jizo is here, mo...

rows.label: qst101803_msg0024
rows.name:
It's no use, mo... My heart
can't reach Jizo, mo.

rows.label: qst101803_msg0025
rows.name: Thank you, mo~

rows.label: qst101803_msg0026
rows.name:
Please take Jizo to
Vahsah in Fons Maim, mo~
